      <byline class="print_byline">By Sabrina Tavernise</byline>
      <byline class="normalized_byline">Tavernise, Sabrina</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Russia's Norilsk Nickel, major producer of platinum and palladium, plans to reorganize in move analysts say will hurt minority shareholders and erode company's value (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Norilsk Nickel, a metals producer, plans to reorganize in a move analysts said would hurt minority shareholders and erode the company's value. Norilsk is a major world producer of platinum and palladium.</p>
        <p>Sabrina Tavernise (NYT)</p>
